Use the standard library
This is how to move_one_ball of arr:
  Remember that drops is 0
  Remember that n is arr's length
  Do this n times:
    When item 0 in arr is more than item 1 in arr, then:
      Increase drops by 1
    End when
    Add arr to item 0 in arr
    Remember that i is 0
    Do this diff of arr's length and 1 times:
      Remember that item i in arr is item sum of i and 1 in arr
      Increase i by 1
    End do
    Remember that item diff of arr's length and 1 in arr is item 0 in arr
  End do
  When drops is at most 1, then:
    The answer is 1
  But, if not:
    The answer is 0
  End when
